Use open source program Grobid to parse a research paper into metadata
We are using a web service mode. (We can also use batch mode)
Usage:
Step 1: Installation:
https://grobid.readthedocs.io/en/latest/Install-Grobid/

Step 2: Setup webserver
https://grobid.readthedocs.io/en/latest/Grobid-service/
Failed: 2023.May.06: problem of server

Step 2: Use batch mode
https://grobid.readthedocs.io/en/latest/Grobid-batch/




